gth}</strong>{diff.added.map(n=><p key={n.id}>＋ {n.data.label}</p>)}</div><div className="diff-card removed"><small>删除节点</small><strong>{diff.removed.length}</strong>{diff.removed.map(n=><p key={n.id}>－ {n.data.label}</p>)}</div><div className="diff-card changed"><small>连线变化</small><strong>{Math.abs(diff.edges)}</strong><p>{diff.edges>=0?'＋':'－'} {Math.abs(diff.edges)} 条连接</p></div></div>:<div className="empty">请选择两个有效版本</div>}<div className="config-diff"><h3>配置与发布说明</h3><div><span>V{a}</span><p>{va?.note}</p></div><div><span>V{b}</span><p>{vb?.note}</p></div><pre>{`节点结构: ${va?.nodes.length} → ${vb?.nodes.length}
连线数量: ${va?.edges.length} → ${vb?.edges.length}
条件规则: amount > 5000
审批来源: 直属主管`}</pre></div></section></div></>}

